-- sql --
SELECT mapFilter((k, v) -> NOT (k IN (?, ?)), `Attributes`), sum(`Value`) AS `total` FROM (SELECT * FROM `otel_metrics_gauge`) GROUP BY mapFilter((k, v) -> NOT (k IN (?, ?)), `Attributes`)
-- args --
[0] string = "instance"
[1] string = "pod"
[2] string = "instance"
[3] string = "pod"
-- chplan --
Aggregate groupBy=[mapWithout(Attributes, [instance, pod])] funcs=[sum(Value) AS total]
  Scan(otel_metrics_gauge)
